16#ifndef RDATA_IN_1_EID_31_C
17#define RDATA_IN_1_EID_31_C
18
19#define RRTYPE_EID_ATTRIBUTES (0)

21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_in_eid(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23
24 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_eid);
25 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
26
27 UNUSED(type);
28 UNUSED(origin);
29 UNUSED(options);
30 UNUSED(rdclass);
31 UNUSED(callbacks);
32
33 return (isc_hex_tobuffer(lexer, target, -2));
34}
35
36static inline isc_result_t
37totext_in_eid(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
38 isc_region_t region;
39
40 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_eid);
41 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
42 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
43
44 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
45
46 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0) {
47 RETERR(str_totext("( ", target));
48 }
49 if (tctx->width == 0) {
50 RETERR(isc_hex_totext(&region, 60, "", target));
51 } else {
52 RETERR(isc_hex_totext(&region, tctx->width - 2,
53 tctx->linebreak, target));
54 }
55 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0) {
56 RETERR(str_totext(" )", target));
57 }
58 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
59}
60
61static inline isc_result_t
62fromwire_in_eid(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
63 isc_region_t region;
64
65 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_eid);
66 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
67
68 UNUSED(type);
69 UNUSED(dctx);
70 UNUSED(options);
71 UNUSED(rdclass);
72
73 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &region);
74 if (region.length < 1) {
75 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
76 }
77
78 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, region.length));
79 isc_buffer_forward(source, region.length);
80 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
81}
82
83static inline isc_result_t
84towire_in_eid(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
85 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_eid);
86 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
87 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
88
89 UNUSED(cctx);
90
91 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
92}
93
94static inline int
95compare_in_eid(ARGS_COMPARE) {
96 isc_region_t r1;
97 isc_region_t r2;
98
99 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
100 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
101 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_eid);
102 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
103 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
104 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
105
106 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
107 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
108 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
109}
110
111static inline isc_result_t
112fromstruct_in_eid(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
113 dns_rdata_in_eid_t *eid = source;
114
115 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_eid);
116 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
117 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
118 REQUIRE(eid->common.rdtype == type);
119 REQUIRE(eid->common.rdclass == rdclass);
120 REQUIRE(eid->eid != NULL || eid->eid_len == 0);
121
122 UNUSED(type);
123 UNUSED(rdclass);
124
125 return (mem_tobuffer(target, eid->eid, eid->eid_len));
126}
127
128static inline isc_result_t
129tostruct_in_eid(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
130 dns_rdata_in_eid_t *eid = target;
131 isc_region_t r;
132
133 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_eid);
134 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
135 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
136 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
137
138 eid->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
139 eid->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
140 ISC_LINK_INIT(&eid->common, link);
141
142 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
143 eid->eid_len = r.length;
144 eid->eid = mem_maybedup(mctx, r.base, r.length);
145 if (eid->eid == NULL) {
146 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
147 }
148
149 eid->mctx = mctx;
150 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
151}
152
153static inline void
154freestruct_in_eid(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
155 dns_rdata_in_eid_t *eid = source;
156
157 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
158 REQUIRE(eid->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
159 REQUIRE(eid->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_eid);
160
161 if (eid->mctx == NULL) {
162 return;
163 }
164
165 if (eid->eid != NULL) {
166 isc_mem_free(eid->mctx, eid->eid);
167 }
168 eid->mctx = NULL;
169}

171static inline isc_result_t
172additionaldata_in_eid(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
173 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_eid);
174 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
175
176 UNUSED(rdata);
177 UNUSED(add);
178 UNUSED(arg);
179
180 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
181}
182
183static inline isc_result_t
184digest_in_eid(ARGS_DIGEST) {
185 isc_region_t r;
186
187 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_eid);
188 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
189
190 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
191
192 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
193}

195static inline bool
196checkowner_in_eid(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
197
198 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_eid);
199 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
200
201 UNUSED(name);
202 UNUSED(type);
203 UNUSED(rdclass);
204 UNUSED(wildcard);
205
206 return (true);
207}

209static inline bool
210checknames_in_eid(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
211
212 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_eid);
213 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
214
215 UNUSED(rdata);
216 UNUSED(owner);
217 UNUSED(bad);
218
219 return (true);
220}

222static inline int
223casecompare_in_eid(ARGS_COMPARE) {
224 return (compare_in_eid(rdata1, rdata2));
225}
